    "minorAccountReviewUnder13PublicTitle": "We can't give you an account yet",
    "minorAccountReviewUnder13PublicBody": "Divine isn't built for kids under 13 and the social media rules around the world tie our hands.\n\nA lot of things on the internet push you to lie to get what you want, and we hate that. It's the wrong lesson for life, and we're not going to teach it to you here.",
